-- list-stats-crystal.cell: compute mean of a list, crystallize
-- Tests: arithmetic on list values, sum/len, crystallization

⊢ compute-mean
  given values ≡ [10, 20, 30, 40, 50]
  yield mean

  ∴ Compute the arithmetic mean of «values».

  ⊨ mean = 30

⊢ crystallize
  given §compute-mean
  given compute-mean→mean
  yield §compute-mean', is-faithful

  ∴ Read «§compute-mean». It computes the mean by summing and dividing by count.
    Write a ⊢= expression: sum(values) / len(values)
    Return the crystallized definition and faithfulness.

⊢ verify-crystal
  given §compute-mean'
  given crystallize→is-faithful
  yield approved

  ∴ Does «§compute-mean'» produce 30 for [10, 20, 30, 40, 50]?

  ⊨ approved = true
